5038 <div>

5039 <h1 class="mf-text-title-3-serif" data-gtm-vis-recent-on-screen-59547834_282="121" data-gtm-vis-first-on-screen-59547834_282="121" data-gtm-vis-total-visible-time-59547834_282="100" data-gtm-vis-has-fired-59547834_282="1">

5040 <p>Request an Appointment</p>

5041 </h1>

5042 </div>

5043 </div>

5044 </div>

5045 </div>

5046 <div class="block block-meda-blocks block-spacer">

5047 <div class="mf-spacer mf-spacer--xs"></div>

5048 </div>

5049 <div class="block-layout-builder block-inline-blockrich-text">

5050 <div class="mf-rich-text col-span-full" data-analytics-event="e_componentClick" data-analytics-component-type="rich text" data-analytics-item-title="" x-data="">

5051 <p>It’s helpful to have the following when calling:</p>

5052 <ul>

5053 <li>First and last name, and address</li>

5054 <li>Your relationship to the person seeking care</li>

5055 <li>Telephone number for the person seeking care, plus an emergency contact name and number</li>

5056 <li>Basic diagnosis information</li>

5057 <li>Name of the doctor who referred you to us</li>

5058 <li>Insurance information</li>

5059 </ul>

5060 <p>Care advisors are available Monday to Friday from 8:30am–5:00pm and will help you with next steps. An answering service is available outside these hours and on weekends. We make first appointments available within 72 hours for people who:</p>

5061 <ul>

5062 <li>Suspect they have cancer or are concerned about their cancer risk</li>

5063 <li>Have a cancer

5064 <a href="/cancer/navigating-care/diagnosis">

5065 <strong>diagnosis</strong>

5066 </a> and are looking for a second opinion

5067 </li>

5068 <li>Are referred by a physician to one of our specialists</li>

5069 </ul>

5070 <p>In the event you don’t have a physician referral, we’ll try to collect enough information on the call to schedule an appointment with the right team.</p>

5071 </div>

5092 <p>If you’ve already had an appointment with one of our cancer doctors, a virtual visit may be possible. Please select the

8161 <h2 class="mf-text-title-3-serif text-gray-700">

8162 <p>Doctor video visits offer convenient of face-to-face appointments from home.</p>

8163 </h2>

8164 <div class="mf-text-body-3-sans text-gray-600">

8165 <div class="mf-rich-text" data-analytics-event="e_componentClick" data-analytics-component-type="rich text" data-analytics-item-title="" x-data="">Doctor video visits at Montefiore Einstein are available on any device via the

8166 <a href="https://mychart.montefiore.org/mychart/Authentication/Login?">MyChart app</a> or on a computer using the Chrome or Firefox browser. Your computer or device needs to have a working web camera, microphone, speakers and a high-speed internet connection
